maven based project installation

select maven project 
file > new >

uncheck create a simple project 
location : you can select where you want to create project 
rest u need to ignore just click on next

in catalog select internal 
then select maven-archetype-webapp in second box then next
			
uncheck create a simple project 
location : you can select where you want to create project 
rest u need to ignore just click on next

check for console , whe it says Y:  then press Y

change groupid and artifact Id with project name , in package write only com  then finish


			
			
			
			